  "text": "To obtain the (co)variance component and genetic parameter estimates, the analyses were carried out using the long-chain scheme [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , with a view for evaluating the posterior distribution densities obtained from Gibbs chain samples. The results of variance component and heritability estimates for growth traits, obtained through GS in single-trait analyses are presented in Table 2 .",
